---
title: French Onion Chicken with Thyme-Roasted Potatoes & Carrots
description: Meet French onion soup—chicken-fied! Yep, our chefs went and transformed everyone’s favorite cheese-topped soup into a hearty chicken dinner. The two were basically meant to join forces, and once you try a bite, we think you’ll wholeheartedly agree. Think juicy chicken breasts topped with rich, thyme-flecked caramelized onion and melty mozzarella. On the side, there’s roasted carrots and potatoes for good measure. Bon appetit!
